thread.title: Germany's SPD changes guard to keep chaos at bay

title: Germany's SPD changes guard to keep chaos at bay
text:
Germany's SPD changes guard to keep chaos at bay 10:37pm GMT - 02:05 
Germany's Social Democrats have chosen a new caretaker leader to try to prevent the party sliding into further chaos. The party is riven with disputes over the coalition it formed last week with Angela Merkel's party. Reuters' Paul Carrel reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
